  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of XOMA 052 in Subjects With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus on Stable Metformin Monotherapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo-controlled, Dose-ranging Study of the Safety and Efficacy of XOMA 052 in Subjects With Type 2 Diabetes Mellitus on Stable Metformin Monotherapy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
