  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study hypothesis is that XOMA 052 improves glycemic control in subjects with Type 2
      Diabetes.

      Study X052078 is designed to establish efficacious dose(s) for future studies based on
      improvement in HbA1c.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
